Folks should take a look at the work Bindview did on the Naptha family 
of dos attacks.  Basicly, they found ways to move up the application
stack, consuming CPU, without a serious comitment of resources on the
client side.  razor.bindview.com/publish/advisories/adv_NAPTHA.html

Adam

